{"tid":2142562,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國徵兵現場「美女」如雲似選美大會　絕色變性人竟激似何超蓮","createTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T06:53:59.000Z","uid":137088,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a219d43e39a98962a5fea230c434b3c1a14693e7","tid":2142562,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T13:13:17.000Z","msg":"泰國每年原定4月舉辦徵兵抽籤，不過受到疫情影響，延至8月舉行，變性人雖然不用服兵役，但亦須到現場報到，去年在其中一個會場，就有一名變性選美冠軍現身，艷壓全場。今年不少會場都出現大批跨性別「美女」，成為網上熱話。<br />\n<br />\n有泰國專頁saonaakhom整理出現場出現的「美女」，個個貌若天仙，身材豐滿，悉心打扮，妝容精緻，一不為意，還以為是選美現場，但她們手上拿著兵役單，充滿違和感，不少網民留言說：「都快被混淆了」、「比女人還美」、「真女人看了都自卑」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200806/368028625930424320.jpeg/Or6wSMaGncjyumk_gqRP3gvvDgJqrBSE8spUn_LKVJ8?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200806%2F368028625930424320.jpeg%2FOr6wSMaGncjyumk_gqRP3gvvDgJqrBSE8spUn_LKVJ8%3Fv%3Dw480&h=9f14fe26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/06/ARCIdi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F06%2FARCIdi.png&h=de52d79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/08/06/ZdEI4j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F08%2F06%2FZdEI4j.png&h=62e0d1d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"303ff2d3cb162301d6a55aa63c699d54dbb4b8a8","tid":2142562,"uid":115096,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:13:15.000Z","msg":"頭兩個手掌指節骨都仍然似男人<br />\n第三個手指都似埋女人"},{"pid":"22b2502e502e41e7ff9a32f9beb3e24262ffc524","tid":2142562,"uid":20908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"屌or唔屌？"},{"pid":"db5de5e48bf36356d4cdd1479a2fab0edc794fd7","tid":2142562,"uid":172349,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"係軍營雙人房，佢係你roomate, 你既生活會如何？"},{"pid":"50af